<note n="0443011" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0443011">賜紫臣【大】，〔－〕【明】</note>
<note n="0443012" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0443012">邪【大】，耶【宋】【元】【明】</note>
